edu.spa.ftclib.internal - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal
The main library package; contains several sub-packages and miscellaneous classes
edu.spa.ftclib.internal.activator - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal.activator
Classes to easily "activate" and "deactivate" servos, continuous rotation servos, and DC motors
edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal.controller
General control classes interfaces, PID-type controllers, and a "finishing algorithm"
edu.spa.ftclib.internal.drivetrain - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal.drivetrain
General drivetrain classes and interfaces; and tank, omniwheel, and Mecanum drivetrains
edu.spa.ftclib.internal.sensor - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal.sensor
A standardized sensor framework, a heading helper class, and implementations of several heading sensors
edu.spa.ftclib.internal.state - package edu.spa.ftclib.internal.state
Button and toggle code to encapsulate the logic behind commonly-used tele-op controls
edu.spa.ftclib.sample - package edu.spa.ftclib.sample
Examples of how to use the library
edu.spa.ftclib.sample.opmode - package edu.spa.ftclib.sample.opmode
Example op-modes
edu.spa.ftclib.sample.robot - package edu.spa.ftclib.sample.robot
Example Robot subclasses
edu.spa.ftclib.util - package edu.spa.ftclib.util
Utilities not part of the main library
